message: "If you use this repository, please cite it using the metadata below and cite the associated manuscript when available."
title: "Scaffold-Local Fragment-Additivity Breakdown in Coumarin logP Prediction: DFT-Supported Reliability Triage for Medicinal Chemistry Decision-Making"
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: "GÜNEŞ"
    given-names: "Ahmet"
