license: MIT
abstract: "Journal-neutral reproducibility repository containing curated coumarin logP benchmark data, external comparator outputs, SangsterLogP audit files, DFT/MEP panel files, figures, scripts, and checksums for a reliability-triage analysis of fragment-additivity breakdown in coumarin logP prediction."
keywords:
